<article>
    <h1>The Penny Dreadful 500</h1>
    <section>
        <ul>
            <li>End of season tournament</li>
            <li>500 tix in prizes</li>
            <li>Free entry</li>
            <li>The next Penny Dreadful 500 is on {{next_pd500_date}}</li>
            <li>Sign up is on <a class="external" href="https://gatherling.com/eventreport.php?event=The%20Penny%20Dreadful%20500">Gatherling</a></li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>New to Penny Dreadful?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Check out the <a href="{{faqs_url}}">FAQs</a></li>
            <li>Play for free with the <a href="{{cardhoarder_loan_url}}">Cardhoarder Free Loan Program</a></li>
            <li>Join the Penny Dreadful community on <a href="{{discord_url}}">Discord</a></li>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>{{_ Prizes}}</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th class="n">Finish</th>
                    <th class="n">Prize</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="n">1st</td>
                        <td class="n">130 tix</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="n">2nd</td>
                        <td class="n">90 tix</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="n">3rd-4th</td>
                        <td class="n">60 tix</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="n">5th-8th</td>
                        <td class="n">30 tix</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="n">9th-16th</td>
                        <td class="n">10 tix</td>
                    </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <p>Prizes from our sponsor <a class="external" href="https://www.cardhoarder.com/">Cardhoarder</a> in credit.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Byes</h2>
        <p>Players who win a <a href="{{tournaments_url}}">tournament</a> this season receive a round one bye.</p>
        <p>The following players have earned a bye in the Penny Dreadful 500.</p>
        <ul>
            {{#people_with_byes}}
                <li><a href="{{url}}">{{person}}</a></li>
            {{/people_with_byes}}
        </ul>
    </section>
</article>
